data.text:
These figures (angels, fairies and mermaids) are made locally, using a mix of mainly merino and english hand dyed wool tops,sometimes embellished with more exotic fibres (silk, baby camel down and baby alpaca). They are mostly needle felted, with a few stitches added when needed. (and a thread on each one so that they can be used as a hanging decoration).

Each figure is individually crafted so there will be slight variations with each one. Approx. 16 cms long

*Price is for one*
